toplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808330/extras/c83c761717f67d81c152f0e62796ec13.poster.avif?t=1690856038\" width=360 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808330/extras/c83c761717f67d81c152f0e62796ec13.webm?t=1690856038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808330/extras/c83c761717f67d81c152f0e62796ec13.mp4?t=1690856038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 Players Local Multiplayer<br></li><li>Adventure Mode<br></li><li>Massive enemy<br></li><li>Four playable characters</li></ul>",
